  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个序列图，描述开发者如何通过一个统一模块来完成代码生成和优化的完整流程。这个模块我暂时叫它\"Combined Module (HealthTech_EMR_Sync)\"，它不只是生成代码，还要能自我监控、自我修复。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Developer",
        "Combined Module (HealthTech_EMR_Sync)",
        "Initiate Code Generation Request"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，所以开发者先发起请求，然后模块内部处理生成。我想确认一下：模块处理完之后，是直接把代码返回给开发者，还是先经过一轮内部审查？我看到流程里有个\"Submit Generated Code for Review\"的动作。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Deliver Generated Code",
        "Submit Generated Code for Review"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，开发者收到代码后要提交回来做审查，但这个审查其实是模块自己执行的——Perform Error Analysis，然后还有一个分析检测的备注说明。所以是模块内部的闭环，不是人工审查。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Submit Generated Code for Review",
        "Perform Error Analysis",
        "Analyze and Detect Errors"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把前半部分画出来：开发者发起请求，模块处理并返回代码，开发者再提交审查。接下来您提到的自我监控和自我修复，这部分是并行的还是顺序的？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Initiate Code Generation Request",
        "Process Code Generation",
        "Deliver Generated Code",
        "Submit Generated Code for Review",
        "Perform Error Analysis"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是顺序的三步：先Self-Monitor System Performance监控性能，然后Apply Self-Healing and Bias Reduction执行自我修复和偏差消除，最后才把优化后的代码反馈给开发者。每一步都要有备注说明，特别是最后一步要强调\"Continuous Self-Optimization\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Self-Monitor System Performance",
        "Monitor and Optimize Performance",
        "Apply Self-Healing and Bias Reduction",
        "Continuous Self-Optimization",
        "Provide Feedback and Optimized Code"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "清楚了，所以模块内部有三段自循环：错误分析、性能监控、自我修复，最后虚线返回给开发者。开发者那边需要有什么备注吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Self-Monitor System Performance",
        "Apply Self-Healing and Bias Reduction",
        "Provide Feedback and Optimized Code"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "需要，最后加一个备注在开发者那边：Review and Use Optimized Code。这样整个流程就闭环了——从请求发起到最终使用优化代码。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Review and Use Optimized Code"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成了。整个序列图现在包含：开发者与Combined Module (HealthTech_EMR_Sync)之间的三次交互，模块内部三个自处理步骤，以及四个关键备注点。您看一下是否符合预期？",
